  <slide>
    <title>Use of Color: Color alone to convey information</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Using color as the only way to convey information (<a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG21/#use-of-color" target="_spec">WCAG 1.4.1</a>).</li>
        <li>1 in 6 men have some form of color blindess.</li>
        <li>Older people and people with many types of visiual impairements often lose the ability to perceive colors.</li>
        <li>Colors can also can mean different things in various cultures.</li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
  </slide>

